{"word":"Ashtoreth","slug":"ashtoreth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ashtoreth</b> <a href=\"#/H6253\">H6253</a> <br/> An idol of the Philistines, Zidonians, and Phenicians.<br/> Probably identical with Queen of Heaven<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=7&verse=18'>Jer 7:18</a><br/> Worshiped by Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=13'>Jdg 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=10&verse=6'>Jdg 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=4'>1Sa 7:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=12&verse=10'>1Sa 12:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=5'>1Ki 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=33'>1Ki 11:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a><br/> Temple of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=10'>1Sa 31:10</a><br/> High places of, at Jerusalem, destroyed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Ki 23:13</a>"}]}